GreaterChina Professional May Buy 20% of Investor Relations Firm

-- B y   J a m e s   R e g a n
-- 
2011-07-17T10:25:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/greaterchina-professional-may-buy-20-of-investor-relations-firm.html
GreaterChina Professional Services
Ltd. said it is considering buying a 20 percent stake in a
company that provides investor-relations services.  A memorandum of understanding regarding the possible
investment has been signed, it said in a statement to the Hong
Kong Stock Exchange. The target company was not named and no
details regarding the consideration were released.  To contact the reporter on this story:
James Regan in Hong Kong at 
